<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #FEFCFF">

    <div class="container" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #F1F7ED; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">Dear <strong>@Model.Email</strong>,</p>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
