        </p>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            To get started, register on our platform by clicking the button below:
            <br>
            <a href="@Model.Url" style="padding: 5px 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #E5EAFA; text-decoration: none; background-color: #1B2845; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 230px; display: inline-block;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#3A4E78'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#1B2845'">Join up</a>
